</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Mr Vitaly Churkin, Russia's representative on the Bosnia 'contact group',
said yesterday the group was intending to recommend that the United Nations
Security Council discuss the gradual lifting of sanctions against Serbia.
British officials, however, said they would consider 'a gradual lifting of
