<HEADLINE>
FT  06 SEP 94 / UK Company News: Plasmec recovers to Pounds 352,000
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Pre-tax profits at Plasmec, the electronic and electrical equipment
manufacturer, made a sharp recovery for the six months to June 30 to Pounds
352,000 against a loss of Pounds 237,000.
Turnover was up from Pounds 5.96m to Pounds 7.23m, boosting operating
profits to Pounds 642,000.
The USM-quoted company doubled the interim dividend to 1.5p. Earnings per
share were 4.8p (3.6p losses).
</TEXT>
